            "title": "西區副食品批發市場發泡膠箱起火 濃煙衝天消防拖喉救熄",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"西區副食品批發市場發泡膠箱起火 濃煙衝天消防拖喉救熄。FB：西環變幻時\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9de4bdf6b5a2c82095b644e2a90e7834/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250205/_2025020521441696945.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">西區副食品批發市場發泡膠箱起火 濃煙衝天消防拖喉救熄。FB：西環變幻時</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西環豐物道8號西區副食品批發市場對開街頭，今日（2月5日）晚上9時許，有發泡膠箱起火，濃煙衝天，消防接報趕至，動用一喉一煙帽隊灌救，迅速將火救熄，起火原因仍在調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4061877/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場濃煙衝天。FB：西環變幻時\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5b8c042ff9cb176149865e436c4d1633/2025-02/videoframe_3718.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場濃煙衝天。FB：西環變幻時\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4061878/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"街道煙霧瀰漫。FB：西環變幻時\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9ea232b4b3e376b004dc16ef14403da2/2025-02/476273395_10170805487720261_4462115055294776288_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        街道煙霧瀰漫。FB：西環變幻時\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
